channel.title: Interview with John Doherty
channel.description:
Hey guys - so I have joined #TeamYetAnotherBootstrapperInterviewPodcast with my first interview of another bootstrapper on my personal podcast: http://podcast.kalenjordan.com/e/interview-with-john-doherty/
He's a pretty interesting guy and is at a similar stage to many people on this forum - although he's growing insanely fast (I got a tiny bit jealous not gonna lie).
Would be cool to hear what you guys think about it.
